Make your beer even more enjoyable with this sleek app that will make it simple to snap a pic of your beer and take tasting notes. Rate your experience and add other information to use as a reference in the future. Share your notes with your friends on Facebook and Twitter. 

Beer Bro has an understated and intuitive interface. Dropbox syncing and backup features come built-in so you can be sure your notes are safe. 

Beer Bro is totally customizable. You can tweak your beer journal, or even create entirely new journals if you like. 

CUSTOMIZE BEER BRO

If you want something like this app, but just a little different or for a different kind of item Beer Bro is the iPhone app for you! 

Customization is built into Beer Bro so you can create your own kinds of lists with any controls that you want.  You can also modify existing lists or change how they behave. 

Here are some of the controls you can build with: 
- Small text cells, multi-line text cells, lists, rating sliders, 5 star ratings pickers 

Even more controls! 
- web page linker 
- date control 
- a picture control (to use the camera or your photo library) 
- a currency and a number field 

Powerful searching and browsing features are built into Beer Bro so that finding your information is a snap. 

Beer Bro will also allow you to send any tasting note as an email, tweet or Facebook post.

If you like to keep any type of tasting notes journal, Beer Bro is the iPhone app for you! 

TECHNICAL NOTES 

- Analytics 
- - Beer Bro anonymously collects usage information